N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4111.19 - Void entries

State Regulations

All entries not governed by published conditions shall be
void and no deviation from such published conditions shall be permitted. Any
nominator who is allowed privileges not in accordance with the published
conditions of the race, or that are in conflict with this Subchapter, shall be
debarred from winning any portion of the purse. Notes
